      <prop type="x-translation-ref">羔羊.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>羔羊之皮，素絲五紽，退食自公，委蛇委蛇。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>[Those] lamb-skins and sheep-skins,
With their five braidings of white silk!
They have retired from the court to take their meal;
Easy are they and self-possessed.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
